                    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">Conference &lsquo;Together for Health&rsquo; 2026: what the signals mean for health technology</h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">On March 15, 2026, policymakers, healthcare executives and technologists gathered at the &lsquo;Together for Health, Care and Wellbeing&rsquo; conference. The message was clear: healthcare must fundamentally change. What does this mean for healthtech investors?</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-white/50">
